{"tid":17950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女大生用高潮按摩棒鬧鐘　天天上課不遲到","createTime":"2016-12-02T04:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T17:33:58.000Z","uid":11680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc86250a39009eb55bf9617902f2e9e195cc966d","tid":17950,"uid":11680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:37:46.000Z","msg":"就讀美國康乃狄克大學(University of Connecticut)分子生物學的女大生芬博格(Samantha Feinberg)說，自從她使用了按摩棒鬧鐘之後，讓她每天都從高潮中醒來，而且早上9點的課，她也不再因為貪睡而遲到。<br />\n <br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，芬博格說，她花了約新台幣3千元，買了這個性玩具鬧鐘「Little Rooster」。以前的她都會貪睡，不管鬧鐘聲響，但現在她使用這款按摩棒鬧鐘後，每天早上都會經過一番高潮的洗禮，讓她從睡夢中覺醒，她形容：「現在我起床的模式改變了，但真的很棒。起床不再是一項煩人的例行工作，這反而是一個讓人舒壓的好物。」<br />\n <br />\n「Little Rooster」鬧鐘在設定時間的前5分鐘，就會開始緩慢震動，在震動5分鐘後讓使用者達到高潮，這時也會讓使用者準時起床。芬博格就說：「現在每天早上起床，都讓我好高潮、好興奮！」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n完整新聞連結:<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161202/1002494/女大生用高潮按摩棒鬧鐘%E3%80%80天天上課不遲到\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20161202%2F1002494%2F%E5%A5%B3%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A8%E9%AB%98%E6%BD%AE%E6%8C%89%E6%91%A9%E6%A3%92%E9%AC%A7%E9%90%98%25E3%2580%2580%E5%A4%A9%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%B2%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%B2%E5%88%B0&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=29d20be4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161202/1002494/女大生用高潮按摩棒鬧鐘%E3%80%80天天上課不遲到</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/02/123739_73865f043cd336ac98dbc3ab30c21127.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F02%2F123739_73865f043cd336ac98dbc3ab30c21127.jpg&h=8707e707&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/02/123739_4ce6302762f052782cd2f03b4b949d46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F02%2F123739_4ce6302762f052782cd2f03b4b949d46.jpg&h=e0e893b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/02/123740_4ce6302762f052782cd2f03b4b949d46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F02%2F123740_4ce6302762f052782cd2f03b4b949d46.jpg&h=f4c90d13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9459938c971592e5f4560d39cec4dc0242daa924","tid":17950,"uid":25969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:38:35.000Z","msg":"U sure是新聞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770d5b81ded22c4216787ef99bc8735548cd3638","tid":17950,"uid":11680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>U sure是新聞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見佢擺係即時新聞既國際版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  定我擺去成人台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d58ead8d865b0aebfbc868a31a025be8f8f34b1","tid":17950,"uid":35749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:49:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>U sure是新聞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n.......so exciting"},{"pid":"6cb5d1aad1f400cdd106c9c0711da262ebdd324c","tid":17950,"uid":5734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"估到施旖婕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78b6fc8e22c8285a2e12023872f8248ba723bf7","tid":17950,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:00:39.000Z","msg":"有冇屎忽版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da78e9a72e3e1a085066b80ecff6ae86d737e7d8","tid":17950,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:01:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇屎忽版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blo